gory:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2012 films]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use Indian English|date=December 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2015}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name = Lovely\n| image = Lovely poster.jpg\n| alt =\n| caption = Film poster\n| director = [[B. Jaya]]\n| producer = {{plainlist|\n*[[R. R. Venkat]]\n*B.A. Raju\n}}\n| writer = B. Jaya\n| starring = {{plainlist|\n*[[Aadi (Telugu actor)|Aadi]]\n*[[Shanvi]]\n}}\n| music = [[Anoop Rubens]]\n| cinematography = S. Arun Kumar\n| editing = B. Jaya\n| studio = {{plainlist|\n*R. R. Movie Makers\n*RJ Cinemas\n}}\n| distributor = [[R. R. Movie Makers]]\n| released = {{Film date|df=yes|2012|3|30}}<ref name=\"ref1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.muvi.com/movies/lovely|title=Lovely Release Date|publisher=muvi.com|accessdate=24 June 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208162525/http://www.muvi.com/movies/lovely|archive-date=8 December 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n| runtime =\n| country = India\n| language = Telugu\n| budget = {{INRConvert|10|c}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.muvi.com/movies/lovely|title=Lovely Budget|publisher=muvi.com|accessdate=24 June 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208162525/http://www.muvi.com/movies/lovely|archive-date=8 December 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n| gross =\n}}\n\n'''''Lovely''''' is a 2012 [[Telugu-language]] [[romantic comedy]] film written and directed by [[B. Jaya]]. The film was produced by B. A. Raju and [[Anoop Rubens]] has composed the music for the film. The film stars [[Aadi (Telugu actor)|Aadi]] and [[Shanvi Srivastava]] in the lead roles. The film was a joint production between [[R. R. Movie Makers]] and RJ Cinemas. Alongside direction, both editing and screenplay were also handled by B. Jaya. The Movie was released on 30 March 2012<ref name=\"ref1\" /> and was a hit at the box office.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.manatelugu.in/2012/06/tollywood-hits-flops-in-first-half-2012.html|title=Tollywood Hits & Flops in First Half 2012|publisher=manatelugu